{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_8_level_main_08-10_beg","storyGroup":"main_8","storySort":20,"storyDependence":"main_8_level_main_08-09_end","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"R8-9","storyName":"相逢，总是离别","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"得知纠察队位于西边，阿丽娜前往东边村子交换物资。在她走后，塔露拉收到有过交易的西边村子正遭搜查的消息，决定伏击纠察队。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_08-10_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_08-10","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":18,"next":20,"characters":["阿丽娜","塔露拉","盾卫","感染者战士"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":4,"musicid":0},{"type":"dialog","id":5},{"type":"character","id":6},{"type":"dialog","id":7},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/28/Avg_bg_bg_iceforest_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":9},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":10},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":11},{"type":"text","text":"晖洁：","id":12},{"type":"text","text":"我不知道我还要走多远。","id":13},{"type":"text","text":"我偶尔会听见冬羽们清脆的叫声，那代表什么？是不是说春天快来了？","id":14},{"type":"text","text":"虽然还是很冷，但天气转暖的日子应该不远了。","id":15},{"type":"text","text":"经过三个星期，我们终于又找到了两个愿意和感染者交换物资的村庄。","id":16},{"type":"text","text":"在离他们几公里外的废弃聚居地，我们扎了营，那有不少燃料，能让我们支撑一段时间。","id":17},{"type":"text","text":"树根实在不好吃。不想再听老爷子说什么“很有营养”之类了。","id":18},{"type":"text","text":"12月7日","id":19},{"type":"dialog","id":20},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":21},{"type":"dialog","id":22},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":23},{"type":"text","text":"这条路通向什么地方，我是清楚的。","id":24},{"type":"text","text":"那个终点我们必须走到，就算我走不到，叶莲娜，阿丽娜，还有伊诺他们......也应该能走到。","id":25},{"type":"text","text":"只是我们脚下的路，实在太不分明了。","id":26},{"type":"text","text":"他们会拒绝我们吗？我们不能给他们太多幻想。","id":27},{"type":"text","text":"许一个没法兑现的诺言是种坏事，乌萨斯帝国对面包和被褥的许诺，只是掩盖了他们的暴行与谎言。欺骗就是另一种统治的开始。","id":28},{"type":"text","text":"他们会厌恶我们吗？很可能。如果不是因为北原上的人民过得都很苦，很多人看见感染者就会向纠察队举报。","id":29},{"type":"text","text":"这种恶意可能是来自他们对于自己处境的担忧......","id":30},{"type":"text","text":"我和博卓卡斯替不一样。我们要防范这些，但这绝对不会是什么他们“骨子里的东西”。","id":31},{"type":"text","text":"我们不能因为这些趋利避害的行为就去恨他们。绝对不可以。","id":32},{"type":"text","text":"他们会伤害我们吗？这我就不太清楚了。我也许不能考虑太多......","id":33},{"type":"text","text":"不管怎么说......我认为，许多人是被逼着变成那样的。","id":34},{"type":"text","text":"如果有阿丽娜那样的老师在，有我们的队伍在，有感染者和普通人的和平共处在......他们会被改变。","id":35},{"type":"text","text":"许多人只是被乌萨斯灌注了太多被歪曲过的观念而已。我们可以帮助他们，知识能够改变人的想法。","id":36},{"type":"text","text":"只不过，这真的很难。即使我相信......在行动中贯彻一种有力的信念，让真相为所有人接受，这本应是最基本的。","id":37},{"type":"text","text":"【上面的话语都被划去了。当然，信件从来没被寄出去过。】","id":38},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":39},{"type":"dialog","id":40},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":41},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/2b/Avg_bg_bg_snowconutry_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":42},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_warm_loop.mp3","fadetime":"3","volume":"0.4","id":43,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":44},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":45},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":46},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"啊，早。","id":48,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"现在出去会不会有些危险？","id":50,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"我问过战士们，纠察队应该都聚在西边的村子吧？前几天你们和他们的交流是不是被发现了？","id":52,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"有这个可能。所以，暂时别往西边去了。","id":54,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"我知道的，那东边这个村子，应该还是可以换些东西的。","id":56,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"哎呀，别太担心，我们以前遇到的情况可比这危险多了。","id":57,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你准备去换些什么？","id":59,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_078_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"罐装水果和干蔬果。","id":61,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......好像不是特别重要的东西？","id":63,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_078_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":64},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"再这样下去战士们会得病的。你也多学点生活方面的常识吧......","id":65,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"填饱肚子都很困难了，有些东西大概真不是那么......","id":67,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#5","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"不对，塔露拉，这可不对。","id":69,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_npc_079_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#5","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"嗯哼，咳——","id":71,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_npc_079_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"“正因为我们有时候吃不饱也穿不暖，所以那些诗歌、音乐、果实、鲜花，对味觉、视觉和嗅觉、触觉的渴望，才是可贵的。”","id":72,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_npc_079_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"“就是这些东西提醒着我们，我们是在为了让所有人过上什么样的生活而奋斗的。”","id":73,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_npc_079_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"健康的身体当然也是其中一部分。一点点蔬果就能让许多人都摆脱疾病了。","id":74,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_npc_079_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#5","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......用我的说法反驳我，很狡诈。","id":76,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_078_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#3","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"什么呀......狡诈是什么词儿啊，不应该哦塔露拉同学。请跟我说，聪——明——！","id":78,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_079_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#3","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"好好。","id":80,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_078_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"需要人保护你吗？","id":81,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_078_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"不太好。我又不是什么特别的感染者，因为我让我们暴露踪迹可不好。而且，我是比较容易隐藏自己身份的感染者，其他的战士们可不容易。","id":83,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"那注意安全。那些村民也没那么值得信任......出尔反尔的事情发生得多了去了。","id":85,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"嗯，好。噢，我会多换点梨的。雪怪们会不会更喜欢苹果？","id":87,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"他们好像更喜欢山莓......就别管他们了吧。他们找那些有自己那一套。","id":89,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我还有个会要开。","id":90,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"好，那我走啦。","id":92,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"——阿丽娜！","id":94,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"什么？","id":96,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"之后我准备组织一个感染者教育小组，你想当组长吗？","id":98,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_078_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"啊，我可以吗？","id":100,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"在那些不是战士的感染者里，你的名声可比我要好。","id":102,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_078_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"那时候也比较容易向大家介绍你了。","id":103,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_078_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"我不是说......","id":105,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"知识的战士也是战士，阿丽娜。这点我会坚持。","id":107,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_078_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"那......","id":109,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"看你安排吧。不会要写演讲辞吧？","id":110,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"啊，我仿佛已经听到掌声了。","id":112,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_078_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#3","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"......别揶揄我了。我去了。","id":114,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_079_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078#2","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"再见。早点回来！","id":116,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_078_2.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":117},{"type":"dialog","id":118},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":119},{"type":"character","id":120},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e6/Avg_bg_bg_snowconutryinside.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":121},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":122},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_nervous_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":123,"musicid":2},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":124},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"这不行。必须直接吊死他们。","id":126,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"大尉他现在不在，如果他在这，一定会立刻这么下令。","id":127,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","name2":"avg_npc_078#4","focus":"2","id":128},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"游击队的战士，我们不是军队，至少现在还不是。","id":129,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"影响太差了。他们本因为信任我们而加入我们，然后因为饥饿而产生怀疑，最后犯下错误。","id":130,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"前提是，我们根本没能兑现承诺。","id":131,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","name2":"avg_npc_078#4","focus":"1","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"承诺让他们吃我们本就不剩下多少的食物？","id":133,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","name2":"avg_npc_078#4","focus":"2","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我们承诺能让感染者有容身之处。","id":135,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......不要指望所有人都是为了崇高的目的来到这里的。这不现实。","id":136,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"如果我们早点交付那批机器得到这些粮食，就能增加他们的信任。","id":137,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","name2":"avg_npc_078#4","focus":"1","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"无论如何我不同意他们继续留在我们的队伍之中。","id":139,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","name2":"avg_npc_078#4","focus":"2","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"那就流放他们。","id":141,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"不准使用额外的暴力，而且，给他们一周的口粮。","id":142,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","name2":"avg_npc_078#4","focus":"1","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"不可能！我们的战士都没有这个待遇！","id":144,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......","id":146,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"这点我们绝不会退让。不是因为功绩什么的，而是因为他们的作为根本不配。","id":148,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"可以。那么，言语别太激烈。别过度斥责他们。","id":150,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"......最多就这样。","id":152,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"好。","id":154,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"西边既然已经有纠察队在活动......那就不能让他们发现这些感染者的踪迹。","id":156,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"那样应该把他们丢在......","id":157,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","id":158},{"type":"dialog","id":159},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorknockquite","id":160},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":161},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"嗯？有人敲门。","id":163,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"请进。","id":165,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":166},{"type":"character","id":167},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":168},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_080","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":169},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"感染者战士","text":"呼，呼......","id":171,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_npc_080.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"感染者战士","text":"塔露拉！","id":172,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_npc_080.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"感染者战士","text":"是纠察队！他们在搜查和我们交易了粮食的那个村庄！","id":173,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_npc_080.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"感染者战士","text":"现在撤退吗？我们现在撤走的话，等他们发现我们的踪迹，我们早就走了！","id":174,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_npc_080.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"——","id":176,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"把纠察队引过来。我们在这附近伏击他们，即使要留下痕迹，我们也应该让纠察队认为这些是我们做的。","id":177,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","name2":"avg_npc_078#4","focus":"1","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"塔露拉！再想想！十公里之内就是第四集团军的岗哨，一旦纠察队报信，他们也会出动！","id":179,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","name2":"avg_npc_078#4","focus":"2","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"如果这两个村庄因为包庇我们而被洗劫......不，不包庇我们也没用，只要他们因为感染者而受害，就不会再有村子会愿意和我们交换物资了。","id":181,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_080","name2":"avg_npc_078#4","focus":"1","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"感染者战士","text":"那把消息截住......","id":183,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_npc_080.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"这种想法会让消息传得更远，更恶劣！","id":185,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"听好，如果你杀了人去掩盖，那么尸体就是新的证据；如果你毁尸灭迹，那么空白就是证据。","id":186,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"想让坏事不要在人和人之间流传，办法只有一个，那就是别让坏事发生。","id":187,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我们现在要做的是拓宽我们的道路，以及愿意继续走下去的后人的路。还有问题吗？","id":188,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"没有。","id":190,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_080","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"感染者战士","text":"你说的也有道理，就这么办。","id":192,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_npc_080.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我们走。","id":194,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"对了，你刚才说的是对的。保护好非战斗人员，帮助他们先撤走。","id":195,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我们有场硬仗要打。这回我和你们一起打这场，而且我们的身边，没有霜星，也没有爱国者；记住，有一天，你们身边可能甚至没有我。","id":197,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"但只要一件事是对的、是可行的，我们身边并不需要任何人。你们并不需要任何人在身边。","id":198,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_080","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"感染者战士","text":"好！","id":200,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_avg_npc_080.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078#5","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"走。","id":202,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f8/Avg_avg_npc_078_5.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":203},{"type":"blocker","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":204},{"type":"image","id":205}],"characters":["阿丽娜","塔露拉","盾卫","感染者战士"]}